{
  "id": "adv_event_2206_01_02",
  "title": "迷子のピース",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "どうしよう、怜ちゃん\n歌詞、全然思い浮かばないよぉ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What should we do‚ Rei-chan?\nI can't think of any lyrics at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 7.105396842999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "ええ……？\nでも、この前は順調に進んでるって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehh…?\nBut last time‚ things were going smoothly…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.3,
      "endTime": 13.0249434471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "うん、大方の歌詞は固まってきたのよ\nただ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ most of the lyrics have been finalized.\nBut…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.3333333333,
      "endTime": 19.666666666700003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "最後のピースが、はまらない\nというか……迷子",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The final piece doesn't fit.\nOr rather… it's lost.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.4333333333,
      "endTime": 26.6533334096,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "最後のピース？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The final piece?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.9333333333,
      "endTime": 28.9924943288,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "サビの出だしに使いたいフレーズがね\nどおお……してもピンとくる詞が降りてこなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a phrase I want to use in the beginning of the chorus.\nNo matter what… I can't come up with lyrics that click.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.3,
      "endTime": 38.099999999999994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "あれでもないこれでもない……って\nもう二日ぐらい悩んでるんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's like this or that…\nI've been agonizing for about two days.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.5333333333,
      "endTime": 44.5133331616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "いわゆるスランプ……だよね？\nクリエイターさんが陥る、世にも恐ろしい現象……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ it's a slump… right?\nA terrifying phenomenon that creators face…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.0333333333,
      "endTime": 53.463899930299995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "なのかな……はぁ\nそういえば、千紗ちゃんと怜ちゃんの方はどう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe… sigh.\nBy the way‚ how about you‚ Chisa-chan and Rei-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.7,
      "endTime": 62.0978002548,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "こっちは順調よ。大枠は固まった\nあとの細かいところは歌詞次第かな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're doing fine. The overall structure is in place.\nThe details will depend on the lyrics.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.6333333333,
      "endTime": 69.5159181913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "衣装も、デザインは固まって\n今、仮縫いをしてもらっているところだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The outfit design has been finalized.\nRight now‚ we're in the process of making the mock-up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.8,
      "endTime": 76.0499998093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "そっか！　二人ともさすがだね！\n衣装もダンスも、完成が楽しみだなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see! You two are amazing!\nI'm looking forward to the completion of the outfits and the dance…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.3,
      "endTime": 84.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃん、さくらちゃん\n私達はそれより先に、歌詞をどうにかしなきゃね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura-chan‚ Sakura-chan.\nWe need to do something about the lyrics before anything else.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.4,
      "endTime": 91.1784126281,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "締め切りまで、猶予はないから\nあまり時間、無駄に出来ない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We don't have any time to spare until the deadline.\nWe can't afford to waste too much time…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.4333333333,
      "endTime": 96.8113605817,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "……はい、そうでした……すみません\nつい目を背けてました……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes‚ you're right… I'm sorry.\nI was just avoiding it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.1,
      "endTime": 104.5399998666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "さくらが現実逃避しかけるなんて、よっぽどね\n……私達も手伝うわよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's quite unusual for Sakura to try to escape from reality.\n…We'll help‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.9666666667,
      "endTime": 111.1057369868,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうだよ！　割り振りはしたけど……\n任せっぱなしにする必要、ないもんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yes! We've divided the tasks‚ but…\nWe don't need to leave everything to you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.3,
      "endTime": 118.3545307716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "ホントに！？　ありがとう！\n……でも、今はまだ大丈夫っ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really!? Thank you!\n…But for now‚ I'm still okay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.6,
      "endTime": 125.33501138679999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.5333333333,
      "endTime": 127.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃん達の言う通り、頼っていいとは思ってるよ\n私達みんなの曲なんだもん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think it's okay to rely on you and Rei-chan‚ like you said.\nIt's our song‚ all of us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.8,
      "endTime": 134.5954423905,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "でも、もうちょっとだけ頑張ってみる！\n怜ちゃん達だって、自分達で頑張ってるんだもん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I'll try a little harder!\nYou and Rei-chan are also doing your best on your own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.8,
      "endTime": 142.7186847687,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "そんなの、気にしなくてもいいのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don't have to worry about that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.9333333333,
      "endTime": 146.6200454076,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "……いや。多分さくら、納得出来ないんだよね？\nここまで来て、安易に人に頼るのが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…No. I think Sakura can't be satisfied‚ right?\nAfter coming this far‚ it's too easy to rely on others.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.8666666667,
      "endTime": 155.8077322641,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "だからとことん、納得いくまで頑張りたい……\nなら、私はそれでいいと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I want to give it my all until I'm completely satisfied…\nI think that's fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156,
      "endTime": 162.26841287620002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.4666666667,
      "endTime": 164.2748526494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "でも、完成しなきゃ元も子もない\nだから、締め切り二日前までに決まらなければ相談して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if we don't complete it‚ there's nothing to gain.\nSo‚ if it's not decided by two days before the deadline‚ let's discuss it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.4666666667,
      "endTime": 172.66666676210002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "……うん、分かった\nそれまではもうちょっと、もがいてみるね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Okay‚ I understand.\nUntil then‚ I'll struggle a little more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.1,
      "endTime": 178.73333333329998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "とは言うものの……\nどうしたらスランプって抜け出せるのかしらねぇ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That being said…\nI wonder how to break out of a slump.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.1333333333,
      "endTime": 185.1806349119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_02-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "あ……この前、デザイナーさんとも話した気がする\nアイデアが詰まった時、どうするのかって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… I think I talked to the designer about it before.\nWhat to do when ideas get stuck.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.5,
      "endTime": 193.9006345749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
